column1:
Everybody dreams of experiencing that rush of adrenaline when you stand atop of a hillock and watch those trees swaying while the water flows down a beautiful stream. Prepare yourself for one such expedition by packing your belongings in the Wildcraft Daypack A4 20 L Backpack. This backpack can be used by both men and women.

Body
This backpack is made of 210D Nylon Ripstop and 420D Nylon Dobby which lend it robustness and durability. The dimensions given to this bag are 279.4 x 482.6 x 152.4 mm in dimension
column2: this backpack compact but can accommodate all your essentials with ease. Weighing 560 g
column3: this bag is lightweight and easy to carry around. With a 20 litre carrying capacity
column4: this Wildcraft Daypack A4 20 L Backpack can accommodate all your essentials such as clothes

column1: Equipped with three compartments and two pockets
column2: this backpack allows you to segregate all your items in order of use. Keeping your load in place and preventing it from shifting around unnecessarily are the sternum straps of this backpack. Ensuring you are comfortable while moving around are the padded shoulder straps and back. Facilitating easy portability of this backpack is the reinforced haul loop which can be used when you don’t want to strap it on. Giving you visibility when it is dark is the reflector tape on this bag. To ensure that you don’t have to stop every time you want a drink of water
column3: this backpack has a hydration bladder compartment and straps for holding hydration bladder. As this Wildcraft Daypack A4 20 L Backpack is <strong>bar tacked on specialised machines
column4: it is resilient to common damages like tearing and ripping.

  • 28 L Capacity
  • Adjustable Shoulder Strap

column1: Life can be stressful at times
column2: and to beat the pressure all you need to do is hit the road and discover an unknown destination
column3:
this will let your mind and body free of all those worldly holds. Pack your belongings in the Wildcraft Pack Y 28 L Backpack and take control of the steering wheel. This bag has been designed for both men and women.

Body

Made of 210D Nylon Double Ripstop and 420D Nylon Dobby
column4: this backpack is durable and resistant to common damages like tearing and ripping. Measuring 330.2 x 508 x 177.8 mm in dimension
column5: this backpack boasts of a slender profile but can fit in all your essentials with ease. Weighing 560 g
column6: this bag is lightweight and can be carried around with ease. With a carrying capacity of 28 litres
column7: this backpack can accommodate your clothes
column9:
equipment and other accessories without much trouble.

Features

column1: A good backpack is equipped with multiple features which help you carry your belongings and at the same time ensure that your comfort is not compromised on. Equipped with two compartments and three pockets
column2: this backpack allows you to segregate all your items in order of use. The side air mesh pockets of this backpack are where you can keep your water bottle or other small accessories. Ensuring that you are relaxed while discovering a new place are the padded shoulder straps and back which provide you with a comfortable carrying experience. For the load management this backpack has been furnished with compression straps at the top and bottom. You can slip in some snacks or accessories in the front flat zippered mesh pocket of this Wildcraft Pack Y 28 L Backpack. This bag has specially designed channels on the back which facilitate a sufficient flow of air. As this backpack is bar tacked on specialised machines it is robust and sure to last you for a longer time. Keeping all your possessions safely encased within are the zipper and buckle closure of this bag.

The side air mesh pocket is where you can keep some accessories which you would want to reach quickly. You can keep some snacks to munch on in the front flat pocket of this compact bag. This bag is going to accompany you on multiple occasions as it is bar tacked on specialised machines.
